videos.description: Trae Young passes the ball behind his back and hits John Collins for the long 3-pointer at the top of the key.

videos.description: Danilo Gallinari's long bucket with 52.5 seconds left ends up being all the Hawks need in a comeback win vs. the 76ers.

videos.description: The Hawks stun the 76ers on the road, thanks to a 15-0 run and a key defensive stop from John Collins, to take a 3-2 series lead.
